WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.370
Proposal templates define how the PDF looks.

00:00:03.370 --> 00:00:05.437
You build it block by block

00:00:05.437 --> 00:00:11.564
header, quote, terms and signature —, drag to reorder, and see the live preview.

00:00:11.564 --> 00:00:15.240
Then each proposal uses the template you choose.
